Can I upgrade/downgrade my account?

You can upgrade or downgrade you account to any plan at anytime, no questions asked.

Can we add more that one user in an account?

Currently we offer plans with single user support only. If you need add more people, you can signup new accounts with Free or Pro plans depending on requirements.

Do you offer any educational discounts?

Currently we don't offer any discounts to students, educational or non-profit institutions.

I have a different question…

Contact us through support chat or via e-mail at support@pilotmail.io

Can I cancel at any time?

There's no minimum contract for PilotMail — cancel at any time without penalty or hassle. Please note that once you cancel you will not eb able to recover your account.
